# The CI build workflow (nationalarchives/tdr-github-actions ecs_build.yml)
# downloads the Wiz CLI binary into the repository root as `wizcli` before
# running `wizcli scan dir .`. Without this exclusion the directory scan reports
# vulnerabilities compiled into the scanner binary itself (e.g. CRITICAL CVEs in
# golang.org/x/crypto embedded in wizcli) rather than issues in this project,
# which causes the scan to fail by policy.
wizcli
